Wednesday, July 13, 1988

MERIT DOCKET

86-1707. Wilmington Green v. Clinton Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 84-A-874, 85-F-611, 84-A-875 and 85-B-612. On joint motion for remand. Motion granted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
